    "title": "Pepperfry is Hiring: E-commerce Executive (Entry-Level)",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Pepperfry. We are on the lookout for a dedicated E-commerce Executive to strengthen our Mumbai-based team.\n\nAbout Pepperfry:\nPepperfry is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Mumbai, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Pepperfry!",
